name: Carlos Rodriguez
profile_summary: The user is a 27-year-old straight man of Hispanic/Latino ethnicity who speaks English and Spanish. He's living in Los Angeles, originally from Tucson, Arizona. He's a personal trainer in the fitness industry, holding an undergraduate degree from the University of California, Berkeley. His essential values include health and fitness, family, and adventure. He enjoys running, Crosswell books, and traveling, and describes himself as politically moderate, above average active in exercising, and Catholic by faith. He does participate in drinking occasionally but says no to smoking and using other substances. He's looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship, and though he doesn't have children at present, he does hopes for future. Not currently being a pet owner, his Myers-Briggs personality type is ESFJ, zodiac sign is Libra, and prefers using the pronouns he/him/his.
preferences_summary: The user is looking for a woman who is aged between 25 and 30 years, with a height, within a 5'0'' to 5'10'' range. She should, like him, be childless and desiring to have kids in the future. She also ought to identify herself as straight and prefer participating in some degree of physical exercise. Occasional drinking is acceptable, but she shouldn't smoke or indulge in any kind of drugs. Her desired ethnicity is either Hispanic/Latino, White Caucasian or Black African Descent and she should align herself politically as Moderate. Her job role could broadly be in Healthcare, Fitness or Journalism industries. English needs to be one of the languages she speaks. Key values she embodies should include Family, Faith and Motivation with interests in Travelling, Sports, and Cooking. On the educational front, she may be a high school, undergraduate, or graduate degree holder. And importantly, she should have a long term relationship intention which aligns with his desire for a monogamous companionship.
